metadata.name: Life in love
metadata.description:
"Keys to dreams" by Elena Artgent is a popular original series created with high-quality paints.

Each piece of the series is a unique abstract snapshot of 
with threads from dreams that extend into real life. 
The threads of the soul are intertwined, bringing with them the secret meanings of dreams, their purpose and power.

This collection is based on the mystery of dreams. A different reality, into which we plunge every night. Sleep is not just a disconnection from reality, but another area of being, a second consciousness, replete with adventures and wisdom… It is a portal between the past, present and future. 

THANKS for your interest in my art!

If you have any questions in mind regarding the artwork please don't hesitate to get in touch as I am always happy to offer advice!
